# Cloudflare static-asset redirects.
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/static-assets/redirects/
#
# Legacy .html paths → extensionless canonicals (301, permanent). These are
# evaluated before asset serving, so they win over the platform's default
# `auto-trailing-slash` 307 (307 → the same extensionless target, but a 301
# passes a stronger canonicalization signal to search engines). Blog URLs are
# already extensionless and need no rule; /404.html has no canonical form.
/index.html / 301
/brisket-calculator.html /brisket-calculator 301
/stall-predictor.html /stall-predictor 301
/fuel-estimator.html /fuel-estimator 301
/cook-scheduler.html /cook-scheduler 301
/contact.html /contact 301
/privacy.html /privacy 301
